{"tid":884760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國起訴 10 名中國情報人員　涉攻擊航空公司竊取機密","createTime":"2018-11-01T00:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-04T09:13:45.000Z","uid":141151,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d27dec5d313cdee561a8d38742f54f28061c04e6","tid":884760,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:33:16.000Z","msg":"美國起訴 10 名中國情報人員　涉攻擊航空公司竊取機密<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/10/31/chinese-spies-sued/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F10%2F31%2Fchinese-spies-sued%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=Vkq%2BgCISrp03aRl07zader%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=cb6ff97d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/10/31/chinese-spies-sued/fun-tech/</a><br />\n<br />\n美國司法部日前表示，決定起訴 10 名隸屬中國國家安全部門的間諜，指控他們入侵航空公司的電腦系統亦意圖竊取航空技術機密。<br />\n<br />\n據外國科技網站 The Verge 引述美國司法部表示，涉事的中國情報人員在超過 5 年的時間內，反覆入侵美國與海外的電腦系統，試圖偷取商用客機所用的渦輪引擎技術。據報有關計畫早於 2010 年初開始，一直持續至 2015 年 5 月。目標是一間正與美國公司合作開發新型引擎的法國航空公司。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，遭指控的中國情報人員 Zha Rong、Chai Meng 隸屬中國國家安全部門江蘇分部，為了獲取技術機密，接連對 2 間法國公司、 8 間美國公司、 1 間澳洲公司以及 1 間英國公司，使用網絡釣魚及惡意軟件等手法進行攻擊。事實上，這已是近 2 個月來，美國政府對中國黑客發出的第 3 間起訴。美國檢察官 Adam Braverman 亦於起訴書上表示，這類由國家支持的黑客活動將直接威脅美國國家安全。"},{"pid":"d588d1f0ed62aa65f46637dcbacab090bf4288ea","tid":884760,"uid":141151,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T00:58:41.000Z","msg":"贏国又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05eeb19ae4eeef9460ff2ca1de95ab624c0b8918","tid":884760,"uid":64290,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T01:00:12.000Z","msg":"自煮研發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bafa3170923a320d0770024210c193d34f4da4ae","tid":884760,"uid":39796,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T01:05:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/11/01/090457_72b53f3562429351b490081e5a597bcf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F11%2F01%2F090457_72b53f3562429351b490081e5a597bcf.png&h=d6e0eb53&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e97bdcf329e3001605b7098af89969ec0c320b56","tid":884760,"uid":92178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T01:06:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eb473ee67332d6bc2b5d4b3df498f0f5f4df17fa","tid":884760,"uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T01:47:48.000Z","msg":"偷雞唔到被起訴，又贏"},{"pid":"36df58d8153a472260f2331fe2d44e820fd98ff7","tid":884760,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:28:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77daba43be4a9e717bfb10f9025a7879cf06cc77","tid":884760,"uid":156652,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-01T09:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/r9gvrjq.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fr9gvrjq.gif&h=a6d77719&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"492eea7240a438d016895e73d4d3f3c6c3cfeedc","tid":884760,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-04T09:13:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}